{"tid":2413724,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"消息指港交所(00388.HK)索諾輝健康(06606.HK)中籤名單查重複認購","createTime":"2021-02-19T02:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T15:05:16.000Z","uid":88664,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"401d34b8fede35f105d04079d089b34908caee60","tid":2413724,"uid":88664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"2021/02/19 09:05<br />\n<br />\n據本地傳媒報道，消息指港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69FQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=78e972d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)  +1.000 (+0.177%)    沽空 $4.61億; 比率 10.784%   向各大券商發出電郵要求提交成功中籤諾輝健康(<a href=\"http://06606.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F06606.HK&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69FQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=a4aabbd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">06606.HK</a>)  -1.050 (-1.250%)   的客戶名單，業內人士估計監管機構擬加強打擊新股重複認購申請。<br />\n<br />\n據悉港交所電郵提出兩大要求，包括是要求券商確保有足夠措施拒絕重複或懷疑重複申請，並需提供所有中籤者的姓名及身份證號碼。(el/t)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2021-02-18 16:25。)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1076958/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1076958%2F1&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69FQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0e7343f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1076958/1</a>"},{"pid":"e955d4bfd614b6d2e3a27bdd74f8c53bd517907f","tid":2413724,"uid":88664,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"好事！B組機會大返"},{"pid":"57132d1e4cef5b8d06039bea71b27480c4af8b0d","tid":2413724,"uid":139319,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"只係阻香港人搵食，大陸嗰班蝗理唔到"},{"pid":"9d54fd6ed416262ef42b03a3287263854d7422d7","tid":2413724,"uid":52684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a